data.description: Welcome to this charming single-level 3-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled in the heart of West Knoxville. This brick and vinyl residence exudes warmth and character from the moment you set eyes on it. With a 2-car garage and an inviting design, it's the epitome of comfortable and convenient living.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-lit interior. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features all the appliances you need, which are thoughtfully conveying with the property. A pantry adds extra storage space for all your culinary needs, making meal preparation a breeze.The large, open living room is the perfect space to relax and entertain.  From the living area, you can access the walk-out deck, which is an ideal spot for enjoying the beautiful Tennessee weather, sipping your morning coffee, or hosting a barbecue with friends and family.The primary bedroom offers a peaceful retreat, complete with an en suite bath for your convenience. This private space provides a haven of relaxation after a long day. The two additional bedrooms are versatile and can be used as guest rooms, a home office, or a playroom, depending on your needs.One of the standout features of this property is the hassle-free, HOA-maintained lawn care, ensuring that your outdoor space remains manicured and well-kept without you having to lift a finger.Built in 2015, this home incorporates modern amenities and energy-efficient features, making it not only aesthetically pleasing but also practical and cost-effective.Location is key, and this residence does not disappoint. Situated in the heart of West Knoxville, it's close to a wealth of amenities. You'll find shopping centers, a fitness center, a variety of restaurants, the YMCA, and access to the Greenway all within a short distance. Whether you want to stay active, dine out, or shop for your daily necessities, you're just a stone's throw away from everything you need.In summary, this 3-bedroom, 2-bath home in West Knoxville offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. With its modern interior, attractive outdoor spaces, and a prime location, it's an inviting and practical choice for those seeking the ideal place to call home in this vibrant community.
